264
00:21:14,102 --> 00:21:16,176
I got one.

265
00:21:17,104 --> 00:21:19,180
He's 22 years old.

266
00:21:24,864 --> 00:21:29,324
When he was nine years old,
he ran away from a fight.

267
00:21:29,410 --> 00:21:34,200
I saw it. I was so embarrassed,
