269
00:21:41,339 --> 00:21:44,043
Well, I made a man out of him.

270
00:21:44,133 --> 00:21:46,837
When he was 16, we had a fight.

271
00:21:48,096 --> 00:21:51,215
Hit me in the jaw. He was a big kid.

272
00:21:53,769 --> 00:21:56,722
I haven't seen him for two years.

273
00:21:59,150 --> 00:22:01,224
Kids.

274
00:22:01,652 --> 00:22:03,726
You work your heart out...

275
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:09,774
- Well, let's get goin'.
- I think we're missing the point.

276
00:22:09,869 --> 00:22:13,532
This boy's the product of a broken home
