01:02:50,813 --> 01:02:53,767
- Number nine?
- Not guilty.

888
01:02:53,859 --> 01:02:56,810
- Number ten?
- Guilty.

889
01:02:57,692 --> 01:02:59,685
Number eleven?

890
01:02:59,780 --> 01:03:01,605
Not guilty.

891
01:03:01,698 --> 01:03:03,773
